# Chef Recommendations

Live Link https://iqramahamed24.github.io/Project1/

Chef Recommendations is a web application that allows users to search for meals based on categories and view their details, including ingredients.

## Features

- Search for meals by category.
- View meal images and details.
- Toggle display of meal ingredients.

## Usage

1. Clone this repository to your local machine.
2. Open the `index.html` file in your web browser.
3. Enter a category in the search box and click the "Search" button to find meals.
4. Click on a meal image to view its details and ingredients.
5. Click the "Show Ingredients" button to toggle the display of ingredients.

## Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## API Used

- TheMealDB API (https://www.themealdb.com/api/json/v1/1)

